before-adding-mods: WARNING! NAME VALUE HAS TO BE THE SAME AS THE MOD FILE NAME, OR THINGS BREAK. (not the .dll or .zip part, just the name like BreadCrumbs)

breadcrumbs.name: BreadCrumbs
breadcrumbs.description: A cute little mod that allows you to feed your goose with the right shift key. When fed bread, geese calm down from whatever they were doing. You can change the bread sprite, the "nom" sound, the key bind and the image size. (2020 Samperson Mod Jam winner!)

quacklua.name: QuackLua
quacklua.description: A Lua API for Desktop Goose mods.

goosemanager.name: GooseManager
goosemanager.description: Manage Goose actions and speed tiers. Now you can finally disable your goose from bringing you memes without an error popping up! (2020 Samperson Mod Jam winner)

label-mod.name: Debugoose
label-mod.description:
CodeF53's Debugging tool.
 - Shows console output while goose is running
 - Saves full console output to log.txt
 - Other debugging info 
PM CodeF53#0241 to request features

Sonigoose.name: Sonicgoose
Sonigoose.description: Turn your goose into fast blue hedgehog from game! It requires to go quick!

goose-lua.name: GooseLua
goose-lua.description: Make mods in Lua. Currently not stable version.

draggoose.name: DragGoose
draggoose.description: Drag your goose around, and take them on to a merry-go-round. May or may not make the goose angry.

clicker.name: Clicker
clicker.description: Have you ever wanted to make your goose become even more chaotic? This mod lets the goose be able to click things! Now will it be able to help you play CS:GO? Probably (not).

hatgoos.name: HatGoos
hatgoos.description:
"give your goos a hat (or your hat a goos if you prefer)" - DaNike, creator of HatGoos
 The greatest mod (in my opinion). Customize your hat. Make your goose have a knife. A baseball cap. Anything. (2020 Samperson Mod Jam winner!)

discogoose.name: DiscoGoose
discogoose.description: Think your goose is boring? Now, your goose will flash different colors! Disco ball goose.

necc.name: NECC
necc.description: NNNNNNNNNNNNNNNNNNNNEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEECCCCCCCCCCCCCCCCCCCCCCCCCCCCCCCCC. Goose have long neck. Very long NNNNNNNNNNNNNNNNNNNNNNNNEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEECCCCCCCCCCCCCCCCCCCCC

ball.name: BallModv1.0
ball.description: Goose ball. Goose can play with ball. Goose chase ball! Wholesome goose?

toys.name: ToysModv1.1
toys.description: Toys for Goose! Ball? Check! Stick? Check! Bed? Less awesome still Check!

shaggymenu.name: ShaggysGooseMenu
shaggymenu.description: Config.ini but easier! And on launch. cool and good

shaggynamemod.name: ShaggysNameMod
shaggynamemod.description: Give your goose a nametag! Now your sonicgoose is complete. Lots of colors!

honcker.name: Honcker
honcker.description: Honk honk! Make your goose honk at will with the F key! Honk honk honk honk

portalgoos.name: PortalGoos
portalgoos.description: Portal gun for your goos! Place portals by holding p and pressing either 1 or 2.
